∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : Path ℂ},
  IsHolomorphic f → γ.IsClosed → ShoIntegral f γ = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Path ℂ),
  γ.isClosed → (∮ z in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Circle C₀),
  HolomorphicOn f (Set.Univ : Set ℂ) → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {U : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup U] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ U] {f : ℂ → U} {γ : ℂ → ℂ},
  IsHolomorphic f → IsClosed γ → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Path ℂ),
  (∀ z : ℂ, Complex.DifferentiableAt ℂ f z) → γ.isClosed → ∮ z in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {f : ℂ → E} {γ : Path ℂ},
  (∀ z : ℂ, HolomorphicAt ℂ f z) → γ.is_closed → PathIntegral f γ = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Path ℂ),
  IsHolomorphic f → γ.IsClosed → ∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z = 0

∀ {U : Type u_1} [inst : TopologicalSpace U] [inst_1 : ComplexManifold U] (f : U → ℂ) (γ : Path U),
  IsHolomorphic f → γ.IsClosed → ∮ (z : U) in γ, f z = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] (f : ℂ → E) (γ : Path ℂ),
  γ.IsClosed → (∮ (z : ℂ) in γ, f z) = 0

∀ {E : Type u_1} [inst : NormedAddCommGroup E] [inst_1 : NormedSpace ℂ E] {γ : Path ℂ ℂ},
  (∀ z, Complex.DifferentiableAt ℂ (γ z)) → (∮ z in γ, γ z) = 0
